creator: Pluggo Pty Ltd
descriptionHtml:
Plug is a platform for friends to organise micro-events or "plugs". With Plug, you can invite people to day-to-day activities as well as manage it all in one place.

Use Plug to:

• Create plugs and invite specific friends to join
• Receive plug invites from your friends

Note: This is still an MVP of our vision and there is much more to come.

Feel free to get in touch with us at:
